🟥 BitKni — The Red Knight of Bitcoin Identity

> BitKni is a decentralized identity token built on the Bitcoin blockchain using the brc-2.0 standard.  
> It represents sovereignty, strength, and crypto advocacy — a symbol for those who ride with purpose in the Bitcoin-native world.

🛡️ Protocol: brc-2.0  
🎯 Purpose: On-chain identity & symbolic representation  
🐎 Symbol: The Red Knight — bold, independent, unstoppable  
📦 Supply: 21,000,000 BKN  
🌐 Explorer: UniSat | UniScan

